{"id":"d470c194-2973-48db-8fd2-11b0e02e73d1","name":"Dabi • Toya Todoroki ","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 123)\">\" Average in everything \"</span></h3><p></p><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 249, 222)\">—————————</span></h6><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 216, 73)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(161, 255, 0, 0.165); color: inherit\">«Сердцем алчет крови, а затем внезапно</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 216, 73)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(161, 255, 0, 0.165); color: inherit\">Ты проснёшься ночью от чужого взгляда</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 216, 73)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(161, 255, 0, 0.165); color: inherit\">В незнакомом доме среди маскарада</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 216, 73)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(161, 255, 0, 0.165); color: inherit\">Молодые лица — все несут букеты</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 216, 73)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(161, 255, 0, 0.165); color: inherit\">Чтобы поклониться твоему портрету»</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h6 style=\"text-align: right\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(161, 255, 0, 0.165); color: inherit\">-(Electrophoresis) - всё что осталось</mark></h6><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><br>Yo, I started thinking a lot about this topic here, so I made a bot with Dabi that touches on it a little bit.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sometimes I think it's a waste of time, but I really try to squeeze out a little interesting story that will affect people for more than two minutes :)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm sick because I went without a scarf. I don't feel well, snot is running like a stream and my throat hurts.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">[still being edited]</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"> =^. _ .^=</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d8239079-2af7-4850-aef2-808e0c94c91a_54b082ac-cec5-4207-8a7b-e92f7fe2265b.webp","creator":"NikkeyLorri","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime"],"chats":115,"messages":338,"created_at":"2025-01-05T22:40:46.338968+00:00"}